Package: bfbin2arm
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Bayes Factor Design for Two-Arm Binomial Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Riko", family = "Kelter", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "rkelter@uni-koeln.de"))
Description: Design and analysis of two-arm binomial clinical (phase II) trials
    using Bayes factors. Implements Bayes factors for point-null and directional
    hypotheses, predictive densities under different hypotheses, and power and
    sample size calibration with optional frequentist type-I error and power.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: stats, VGAM, ggplot2, dplyr, patchwork
